description.oldValue: This feature will bring templates front and center when creating a new whiteboard. When starting a whiteboard, users will be able to choose from a selection of templates or explore all templates to pre-populate a new whiteboard. Users can also start from suggested templates from a blank whiteboard.
description.newValue: This feature will bring templates front and center when creating a new whiteboard. When starting from a blank board, users will be able to choose from a selection of suggested templates or explore templates based on a use case to pre-populate a new whiteboard.
